{"tid":1782470,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【討論】懲罰黃色網店","createTime":"2019-12-14T03:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T03:30:12.000Z","uid":291785,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b7fc0ba7f03e625fbb3dad5049e7149511b2fa25","tid":1782470,"uid":291785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T03:40:13.000Z","msg":"是咁的，見大家都討論黃藍實體店比較多，都想討論下幾樣嘢。（歡迎留言補充）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 製作黃藍網店list</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n首先分返行業，然後再分黃藍。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目標: 由聖誕期間開始提升黃店銷售額</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 對黃藍網店不同策略</span></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃+知名度較高網店: 宣傳+幫襯</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">黃+知名度較低嘅網店: 進行聖誕促銷策略+幫襯</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">藍+知名度較高嘅網店: 同11月19日cctvb台慶做法一樣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">藍+知名度較低嘅網店: 唔好幫佢宣傳同埋唔好洗佢版，當冇傳媒報導，又冇人幫襯，嗰間舖頭仔會好快摺㗎喇</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">仲有最近有新成立嘅ig黃店（唔記得左條link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）,專建立黃色經濟圈，大家多加支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n麻煩巴絲提供建議，大家共建黃色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nP牌仔推唔郁，麻煩大家幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e25a78a7dbcfb1ccad48f51089098d1db36db6","tid":1782470,"uid":291785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T03:48:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7eeda75f3ac73369a57b1a8d3fa94ca1988b08a5","tid":1782470,"uid":291785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T05:37:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ab740396e409be0e4569cb53b0d7e1239dcef6fe","tid":1782470,"uid":291785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T10:35:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ff0d305c47f438390195baa259ff6a518f7b42ee","tid":1782470,"uid":291785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T12:46:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2ea4948ca8aa54830d5f4a2db8dde5cb3f58bc36","tid":1782470,"uid":291785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T03:30:12.000Z","msg":"push"}]}